# Welcome to *Minnow*
## An online tool for performing a systematic literature review

Minnow organizes your *systematic literature review* with
- multiple consecutive *stages*, each narrowing your body of included documents
- multiple *reviewers* per stage, independently assesing your documents for inclusion or exclusion
- both project-wide and individually defined *exclusion criteria*
- customized domain-specific *questions* to gather additional data at each stage
- detailed *agreement reports*, providing a breakdown of statistics about reviewers' assessments


